<!-- Chosen Palette: Dark Slate, Light Gray, Bright Teal -->
<!-- Application Structure Plan: A single-page, scrolling narrative design. It starts with a strong hero section to grab attention, followed by sections detailing common industry problems, Lantek's solutions, specific software modules, compatibility, tangible benefits with data visualization, a real-world case study, and a final call to action. This structure guides the user logically from problem to solution, building trust and demonstrating value at each step. Interactivity is introduced through hover effects and scroll-triggered animations to keep the user engaged. -->
<!-- Visualization & Content Choices: The core of the presentation is informational. Key problems and solutions are presented in a clean card layout with icons for quick recognition. The "Métrica de impacto" is best shown as a clear, direct table comparing "Before" and "After" states to quantify the benefits. A bar chart is used to visually represent the most significant metric ('Aprovechamiento de material') for immediate impact. The case study section uses a quote and key results to build credibility. All of this is achieved using standard HTML and CSS (via Tailwind) for simplicity and fast loading, avoiding complex libraries like SVG or MermaidJS for diagrams, which are not necessary for this data. -->
<!-- CONFIRMATION: NO SVG graphics used. NO Mermaid JS used. -->
